THE NONCERTIFICATED PILOT TOOK THE AIRPLANE WITHOUT PERMISSION. HE 
TOLD INVESTIGATING POLICE OFFICERS THAT HE INTENDED TO CRASH THE 
AIRPLANE INTO HIS ESTRANGED WIFE'S HOME. AFTER MAKING SEVERAL LOW 
PASSES OVER THE HOUSE HE ABANDONED THE IDEA, BUT THE AIRPLANE COLLIDED 
WITH SOME WIRES. THE NONCERTIFICATED PILOT REPORTED HE LEARNED TO FLY 
USING A COMPUTER FLIGHT SIMULATOR PROGRAM AND FLYING RADIO 
CONTROLLED MODEL AIRPLANES. 
 THE NONCERTIFICATED PILOT'S UNWARRANTED LOW FLYING. 
